========================================================================
                             DATA DICTIONARY
                     Floral E-Commerce Website - Florish
========================================================================

Entity: USER
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Field Name     | Data Type   | Key Type | Validation / Constraints
------------------------------------------------------------------------
_id            | ObjectId    | PK       | Auto-generated unique ID
name           | String      | -        | Required, trimmed, max 80 chars
email          | String      | UK       | Required, regex email validation
password       | String      | -        | Required, minimum 6 chars, Bcrypt
role           | String      | -        | Enum: ['user', 'admin'], default: 'user'
createdAt      | Date        | -        | Timestamp auto-created
updatedAt      | Date        | -        | Timestamp auto-updated

Entity: PRODUCT
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Field Name     | Data Type   | Key Type | Validation / Constraints
------------------------------------------------------------------------
_id            | ObjectId    | PK       | Auto-generated unique ID
sku            | String      | UK       | Required, e.g. FL-ROSE-09
name           | String      | UK       | Required, unique, trimmed
category       | String      | -        | Enum: ['bouquets', 'roses', 'indoor', 'lilies']
price          | Number      | -        | Required, positive decimal
oldPrice       | Number      | -        | Optional decimal fallback
description    | String      | -        | Required copy
image          | String      | -        | Host link, default provided
stock          | Number      | -        | Required, positive integer, default 10
isFeatured     | Boolean     | -        | Default: false
rating         | Number      | -        | Floating decimal, default 5.0
reviewsCount   | Number      | -        | Positive integer, default 0

Entity: ORDER
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Field Name     | Data Type   | Key Type | Validation / Constraints
------------------------------------------------------------------------
_id            | ObjectId    | PK       | Auto-generated unique ID
user           | ObjectId    | FK       | Refers to User._id
items          | Array       | -        | List of products, names, quantities
shippingAddress| Subdocument | -        | Name, street, city, pin, phone, email
paymentMethod  | String      | -        | Enum: ['cod', 'online'], default 'cod'
paymentStatus  | String      | -        | Enum: ['pending', 'paid', 'failed'], default 'pending'
totalPrice     | Number      | -        | Combined invoice price
orderStatus    | String      | -        | Enum: ['Processing', 'Shipped', 'Delivered'], default 'Processing'
========================================================================
